title: MusicLine: Collaborative Music Timeline
description: A Next.js application that enables friends to share and discover music through a collaborative timeline with Spotify integration.

title: Instru-Net: Instrument Classification System
description: A deep learning framework that automatically identifies musical instruments in audio recordings using custom neural networks and YAMNet integration.

title: Fuel Cell Performance Prediction Tool
description: A web application that predicts PEMFC performance metrics based on physical parameters using neural network models with intuitive visualizations.

title: Smart Fit: Intelligent Workout Tracker
description: A machine learning system that classifies weightlifting exercises and counts repetitions using motion sensor data for automated workout tracking.

title: Adaptive Daylight Harvesting System
description: An intelligent lighting control system that optimizes energy usage by dynamically adjusting LED brightness and switching between power sources.

title: Seam Carving: Content-Aware Image Resizing
description: An implementation of the seam carving algorithm that intelligently resizes images while preserving important visual elements.

title: Autocomplete Query System
description: An efficient algorithm that suggests completions for partial text input using binary search and weighted ranking of results.
